casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellant, v. Dankworth, Appellee.

[Cite as State v. Dankworth, 118 Ohio St.3d 1210, 2008-Ohio-2234.]

(No. 2007-1211 Submitted April 22, 2008 Decided May 15, 2008.) Gary A. Nasal, Miami County Prosecuting Attorney, and James D. Bennett, Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellant. L. Patrick Mulligan & Associates, L.P.A., Co., George A. Katchmer, and L. Patrick Mulligan, for appellee.

{¶ 1} The cause is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently accepted.

Moyer, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
